title: #129 - Mike Tully & ME
description: Co-Host of the Jason Ellis SHow, Author, & Musician Mike Tully hangs with me in the Mancave to talk about his path from Jersey, to Oxford, weaving through the music industry, writing movies and books with Jason Ellis, and YES we have an ANALOGY OFF...OH and I almost forgot, I play some of his original music!!!
